<h1 class="pagetitle">Chapter 3.2: Editing with WMM</h1>
<p>Windows Moive Maker is Microsoft's basic editing program that comes free with all versions of Windows XP. It is a relatively simple video editing application.</p>
<p>If aren't using Windows XP or prefer a more advanced (and possibly expensive) editing program, check out <a class="wikilink" target="_blank" href="http://MITVWiki.org/Alternative_Windows_Editing_Apps">Alternative Windows Editing Apps</a> in the MITV Wiki.</p>
