<div class="callout important">
<h2>I can't find Windows Movie Maker!</h2>
<p>If you cannot find the Movie Maker application (it should be in the <strong>Start Menu > All Programs</strong> section). you might need to update Windows XP.</p>
<p>To update XP, visit <a target="_blank" href="http://windowsupdate.microsoft.com/">http://windowsupdate.microsoft.com/</a> in Internet Explorer and run all the updates.</p>
</div> <!-- END CALLOUT -->

